               stealing, on the <rs id="t18320405-12-cd79" type="crimeDate">27th of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320405-12-off78 t18320405-12-cd79"></join>, at St. Mary, Islington, 2 lambs, price 4s.
            </rs>, the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18320405-12-victim233" type="victimName">
                     Huntley 
                     Bacon
                  <interp inst="t18320405-12-victim233" type="surname" value="Bacon"></interp>
